kr.ac.mju.islab

Class RewardQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • kr.ac.mju.islab.RewardQuery

  • public class RewardQuery
extends java.lang.Object
    RewardQuery class is a client-side concrete implementation of 'Privacy-Preserving Reward System for Cloudnet' developed by Dae Hyun Yum at August 14, 2016.

    RewardQuery class does query on a server-side concrete implementation, which are RewardServer objects.

    If you are only interested on application, you do not need to check detailed class like RewardScheme.
